abstract: Seattle Storm agrees to multiyear contract with point guard Sue Bird, allowing her to eventually retire from team she has played for her entire career.
lead_paragraph: Bird, a point guard, signed a multiyear deal that should allow her to eventually retire with the Storm, with whom she has spent her entire career.

headline.main: Sue Bird to Remain in Seattle
